content:
Terrible. Absoloutly Shocking. Wouldn't Recommend it to anyone! I exoected 
to be able to set these as my ringtone but in fact you can only play the 
sounds in the app... and they don't even loop. Worthless. I want my money 
back!
Worthless, you can't use the alerts as any ring tone or text tone, it's only for in app use only. Not good for anything. I want my money back.
I love it but I think you can update the tones with better ones because half of them sound so rediculess and not realistic

I only gave it 4 stars because when I had it on my iPhone I was able to send the sounds to my email for ring tones. With this one for the android I do not have that option, please fix and send update.
Tall I can use for ringtones on my phone
I paid for this expecting this too work. Every time I go to open it says sorry this app has unfortunately stopped
If you want me to pay for it, at least let me set it as a ring tone for my emergency text messages. This can be a useful tool, not just a play toy.
Would give five stars if you can set it as ringtone
Awesome fire pager tones specially Motorola Skyfire. The best thing I like in this app is a Simple and easy interface.
